S.FORM: Kenya Gaga kska Meycow ka Kenya, 1 00 N, 38 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 580,367 sq km(hangan na o Tg49)(knlbanga dxgal o 569,140 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 11,227 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 46,790,758 hiyi. Gaga Nairobi ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 12 idas 12 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Kenya ga wada sugan 48.10 ka dxgal qpahan, 6.10 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 45.80 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Uhuru Kenyatta, pnaah hngkawas2013 idas 4 jiyax 9pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
